14
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:13,900
Speaker 6: Was the Angel interested in the human mind?

15
00:02:14,380 --> 00:02:15,740
Speaker 3: I am unable to answer that question.

16
00:02:16,190 --> 00:02:19,120
