41
00:03:25,610 --> 00:03:27,600
Speaker 9: Yeah, boys like that are pretty rare.

42
00:03:31,980 --> 00:03:33,700
Speaker 7: Ray, are things satisfactory?

43
00:03:34,180 --> 00:03:37,060
Speaker 3: Yes. I will be with Dr. Akagi all day tomorrow.

44
00:03:37,660 --> 00:03:39,280
Speaker 3: And the day after that, I will be in school.

45
00:03:39,940 --> 00:03:40,700
Speaker 7: And how is school?

46
