Speaker 12: That second insect had gone crazy.

75
00:04:33,320 --> 00:04:34,780
Speaker 12: General affairs is total chaos.

76
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:37,700
Speaker 8: What do you think happened over there?

77
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:38,920
Speaker 8: It's under investigation.

78
00:04:39,660 --> 00:04:41,560
Speaker 8: Our only clues are these recon photos

