Speaker 8: What's with the grim face?

155
00:08:07,060 --> 00:08:09,980
Speaker 8: Uh, well, it's the Unit 3 activation test.

156
00:08:10,340 --> 00:08:12,300
Speaker 8: We'll be using the fourth as the test pilot.

157
00:08:12,820 --> 00:08:13,320
