Speaker 8: You're kidding! Him?

167
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:46,080
Speaker 8: Yes, well, the prospective candidates have to be kept together for their own protection.

168
00:08:46,460 --> 00:08:47,160
Speaker 8: It can't be helped.

169
00:08:47,900 --> 00:08:48,980
Speaker 8: I don't know how to tell them.

170
00:08:49,580 --> 00:08:50,100
Speaker 8: It's hard.

171
