00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:30,320
Speaker 10: The class bulletin,

192
00:09:30,400 --> 00:09:30,800
Speaker 9: remember?

193
00:09:31,110 --> 00:09:33,080
Speaker 9: You're supposed to deliver this to Miss Ayanami.

194
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:34,100
Speaker 9: Aw,

195
00:09:34,340 --> 00:09:35,860
Speaker 10: come on. Who else has duty?

196
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:38,220
Speaker 10: It's you and Ayanami this week.

197
00:09:38,560 --> 00:09:39,960
Speaker 10: It's Ayanami and me?

198
00:09:40,790 --> 00:09:41,700
Speaker 10: Then I guess I got it.

199
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:45,400
Speaker 10: Huh! But I can't go to some girl's place by myself!

200
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:47,140
Speaker 10: Well, I can go with you!

201
00:09:47,220 --> 00:09:50,040
Speaker 10: Hey! Shinji! Welcome home with me, will ya?

202
00:09:51,270 --> 00:09:52,400
Speaker 10: You know where Iyanami lives, right?

203
00:10:04,360 --> 00:10:07,840
Speaker 18: Uh, uh, mm-hmm.

204
00:10:14,520 --> 00:10:16,860
Speaker 10: Hey, Ray, I'm coming in.

205
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:20,100
Speaker 10: Hey, you can't enter a girl's place without her permission.

206
