Speaker 10: My God.

212
00:10:39,340 --> 00:10:40,980
Speaker 10: This is a girl's room?

213
00:10:41,580 --> 00:10:43,620
Speaker 10: It's so decrepit.

214
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:43,660
Speaker 10: Please.

