00:11:04,800 --> 00:11:06,540
Speaker 10: Well, I won't help you do it.

221
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:08,560
Speaker 10: It's just not manly.

222
00:11:09,020 --> 00:11:09,640
Speaker 11: Well, okay.

223
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:12,520
Speaker 11: But you know, Misato hates guys like that.

224
00:11:13,940 --> 00:11:16,760
Speaker 11: I don't care. It's my policy,

225
00:11:17,100 --> 00:11:17,480
Speaker 10: all right?

226
00:11:20,860 --> 00:11:25,320
Speaker 10: You know, now that I think about it, you've changed.

227
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:26,340
Speaker 10: What?

228
00:11:27,340 --> 00:11:27,860
Speaker 10: You, Shinji.

229
00:11:30,580 --> 00:11:33,700
Speaker 10: The first time I saw you, I really thought you were the world's biggest jerk.

230
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:38,600
Speaker 10: I mean, you sure didn't seem like someone who'd do something for someone else back then.

231
00:11:39,880 --> 00:11:43,560
Speaker 10: I guess you were so deep in your shell that I couldn't see the real you.

